title: Samsung PC Studio 3.0.1 + FLV Converter - Scorpion
description:
With this PC Studio manager you can exchange files between almost any Samsung cell phone very quickly and you can copy important messages and contacts to your computer immediately.

A great program to have if you have a Samsung cell phone. Also, I&#039;ve included a FLV Converter to convert internet video files to cell phone acceptable video files (3GP).

Just un-zip and open the FLV Converter folder and hit &#039;AVI MPEG WMV 3GP MP4 iPod Converter.exe&#039; to launch the converter and hit install.exe in the PC Studio folder to install the PC Suite.

Seed and enjoy - Scorpion.
